            <thetext>The geolocation process will be changed to the following logic:

1. Try to get .address property when user clicks on &quot;Locate me&quot;

2. If it fails, detect closest city from the major cities database (used in the global visualizer + manual city selection page)

3. Invite the user to confirm - or - select another city manually

4. If the user selects another city manually, go back to #3</thetext>
